":0,"quote":{"pid":"80019c9b193dc2d396f76df758dc7f7dce6a6048","tid":662043,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562dbd42e0d94372ca8a8dc4393d9403cc503e80","tid":662043,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:52:50.000Z","msg":"最後3擲一定係head<br />\n咁第3擲係tail<br />\n因為係head就第五擲已經收工<br />\n所以而家係計哂頭兩擲嘅可能性<br />\n0.8 0.8 0.2 0.8^3<br />\n0.2 0.2 0.2 0.8^3<br />\n0.8 0.2 0.2 0.8^3<br />\n0.2 0.8 0.2 0.8^3<br />\n加埋就係答案"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"直接1*1*0.2*0.8*0.8*0.8咪係答案 頭兩次係咩根本唔重要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"樓主唔明嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"Sorry thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded18524e1f08b8403b4d826435e46cc774231e9","tid":662043,"uid":89956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"let Xi be the state where there are consecutive i heads up to that point<br />\nand N be the operator that gives the state after one flip<br />\n<br />\nafter one flip, there are probability of 0.8 that it will go from Xi to X(i+1) and 0.2 chance that it will give back to X0<br />\n<br />\nso N(X0) = 0.8X1+0.2X0<br />\nN(X1)=0.8X2+0.2X0<br />\nN(X2)=0.8X3+0.2X0<br />\n<br />\nwe note that after the game reach the state X3, ie 3 consecutive heads have been observed, the game will end, so <br />\n<br />\nN(X3)=X3<br />\n<br />\nwe can let N be the matrix <br />\n(0.2 0.2 0.2 0<br />\n0.8 0 0 0<br />\n0 0.8 0 0<br />\n0 0 0.8 1)<br />\n<br />\nthen the 4-th entry of (N^j)*(1 0 0 0)^T is the probability of the game is ended on or before j-th move<br />\n<br />\nso the probabilitiy of the game ending exacting on the sixth turn is the 4-th entry of (N^6- N^5)*(1 0 0 0)"},{"pid":"9b309b9d3b6697488b10329ac0f41bd87ed4fd90","tid":662043,"uid":101991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:00:20.000Z","msg":"0.2 * 0.8^3<br />\n<br />\n3rd must be tail. and 4-6 must be head"},{"pid":"49657140ba32d2c8a9b51b03f84c69485fcb1ecf","tid":662043,"uid":45374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1714d66d64e1a24dcdcc5953e39afae038b1e07","tid":662043,"uid":139735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80019c9b193dc2d396f76df758dc7f7dce6a6048","tid":662043,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562dbd42e0d94372ca8a8dc4393d9403cc503e80","tid":662043,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:52:50.000Z","msg":"最後3擲一定係head<br />\n咁第3擲係tail<br />\n因為係head就第五擲已經收工<br />\n所以而家係計哂頭兩擲嘅可能性<br />\n0.8 0.8 0.2 0.8^3<br />\n0.2 0.2 0.2 0.8^3<br />\n0.8 0.2 0.2 0.8^3<br />\n0.2 0.8 0.2 0.8^3<br />\n加埋就係答案"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"直接1*1*0.2*0.8*0.8*0.8咪係答案 頭兩次係咩根本唔重要"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"點解唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:00:58.000Z","msg":"只要第3次係T 尾3係H就直接完<br />\n頭3次出HHT HTT TTT THT 都唔會完<br />\n所以只要計尾4就得 頭兩次可無視 姐係1"},{"pid":"19e98d2e9be3ee817e1c1736037ddb3fa254dd8d","tid":662043,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1714d66d64e1a24dcdcc5953e39afae038b1e07","tid":662043,"uid":139735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80019c9b193dc2d396f76df758dc7f7dce6a6048","tid":662043,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562dbd42e0d94372ca8a8dc4393d9403cc503e80","tid":662043,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:52:50.000Z","msg":"最後3擲一定係head<br />\n咁第3擲係tail<br />\n因為係head就第五擲已經收工<br 